0011D4  1  80 F5           bra @go_ctr_lp
0011D6  1               @go_ctr_done:
0011D6  1               
0011D6  1                  ; wait 300 frames (≈ 5 seconds at 60 Hz) using 16-bit countdown in scratch
0011D6  1  A9 2C           lda #<300
