0015FB  1               ; init_shields — upload 8 damage tiles, set palette entry 7 to dark
0015FB  1               ;   green, init shield_damage counters, write sprite attributes for
0015FB  1               ;   all 4 shields (slots 66–69, base $1FE10).
0015FB  1               ;
0015FB  1               ;   Sprite positions: X = shield_x_lo/hi[n], Y = SHIELD_Y (352)
0015FB  1               ;   Each shield sprite: 32x32, palette 0 (entry 7 = dark green).
